&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;The wearer of the armor takes a -4 circumstance penalty on Diplomacy checks with dragons, but gains a +4 circumstance bonus on Intimidate checks against dragons.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Caster Level:&lt;/i&gt; 24th; &lt;i&gt;Prerequisites:&lt;/i&gt; Craft Magic Arms and Armor, Craft Epic Magic Arms and Armor, &lt;i&gt;protection from energy&lt;/i&gt;,  &lt;i&gt;shapechange; Market Price:&lt;/i&gt; 564,550 gp; &lt;i&gt;Cost to Create:&lt;/i&gt; 283,250 gp + 15,629 XP.&lt;/p&gt;
